<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Swamp Fresh | Trash Bin Cleaning & Pressure Washing</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --blue: #0088cc;
            --light-blue: #e6f7ff;
            --green: #4CAF50;
            --dark: #333;
            --white: #fff;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            background-color: var(--white);
            padding: 15px 10%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        /* New CSS for your uploaded logo */
        .logo-img {
            max-height: 90px; /* You can change this number to make the logo bigger or smaller */
            width: auto;
        }
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 136, 204, 0.8), rgba(0, 136, 204, 0.8)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528323273322-d81458248d40?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80') center/cover;
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        .btn-green {
            background-color: var(--green);
            color: var(--white);
        }
        .btn-green:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .btn-white {
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--blue);
        }
        .btn-white:hover {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .services {
            padding: 60px 10%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--light-blue);
        }
        .services h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--blue);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            width: 300px;
        }
        .card h3 {
            color: var(--green);
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .how-it-works {
            padding: 60px 10%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 10%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="logo.jpg" alt="Swamp Fresh Logo" class="logo-img">
        
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-green" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px;">Call Now</a>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Professional Cleaning for Your Exterior</h1>
        <p>Reclaiming your home’s curb appeal, one bin at a time. Fast, reliable, and affordable.</p>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-green">Book Bin Cleaning</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-white">Get a Pressure Washing Estimate</a>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Trash Bin Sanitizing</h3>
                <p>High-temperature pressure cleaning to eliminate odors and bacteria.</p>
                <div class="price">From $25 / month</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-green" style="display: block;">Select Plan</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Driveway Pressure Washing</h3>
                <p>Remove oil stains, dirt, and mildew to make your driveway look brand new.</p>
                <div class="price">Custom Quote</div>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-blue" style="display: block; background: var(--blue); color: #fff;">Call for Estimate</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>House Washing</h3>
                <p>Safe, low-pressure soft washing for your home's siding and exterior.</p>
                <div class="price">Custom Quote</div>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-blue" style="display: block; background: var(--blue); color: #fff;">Call for Estimate</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
        <h2 style="color: var(--blue);">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card" style="box-shadow: none; background: transparent;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0; color: var(--green);">1</h3>
                <h4>Request & Schedule</h4>
                <p>Pick your recurring bin cleaning plan or call us for a custom pressure washing quote.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" style="box-shadow: none; background: transparent;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0; color: var(--blue);">2</h3>
                <h4>We Do The Heavy Lifting</h4>
                <p>We arrive with professional-grade equipment to blast away grime on your scheduled day.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" style="box-shadow: none; background: transparent;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0; color: var(--green);">3</h3>
                <h4>Enjoy the Clean</h4>
                <p>Step outside to a sanitized, odorless, and sparkling home exterior.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact">
        <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
        <p>Call or text us today for an estimate!</p>
        <h3 style="color: var(--green);">Phone: (555) 123-4567</h3>
        <p>Proudly serving Newberry, Florida and the surrounding areas.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; color: #999;">&copy; 2026 Swamp Fresh. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
